Remark 1.  The classical -matrices for the spin
Calogero-Moser systems were originally found in the 
paper. In contrast to  where the final formulae,
both for the Lax matrix and for the -matrix, were
defined on the elliptic curve only after an additional auxiliary reduction,
our formulae () and () are defined on the 
elliptic curve from the outset.
     

 

