Remark 3.  In obtaining the result () we have only
used the definition of the Dirac bracket and not 
the elliptic function identities which are
unavoidable for checking that () is indeed 
the -matrix for the Lax matrix ().
Of course the functions our procedure yields as series are, as shown in the
Appendix, expressible as elliptic functions.

